====================================

<div class="footer2">
<blockquote cite="">
<b>Resources:</b><br>
<a href="http://spf13.com/post/soap-vs-rest">The Difference Between SOAP and REST</a><br>
<a href="http://www.soapui.org/testing-dojo/world-of-api-testing/soap-vs--rest-challenges.html">SOAP vs REST Challenges</a>
</blockquote>
